<details>
<summary><strong>CLI Conventions & Gotchas</strong></summary>

| Convention | Details |
|------------|---------|
| **OID** | Always use UUID `{{ org.oid }}`, never the org name |
| **CLI Output** | Always append `--output yaml` to all `limacharlie` commands |
| **Timestamps** | API parameters = epoch seconds (10 digits); event data = milliseconds (13 digits) |
| **Enabled/Disabled** | Rules with `enabled: false` are deployed but inactive — review and enable manually |
| **LCQL** | Never write queries by hand — always use `limacharlie ai generate-query` |
| **D&R Rules** | Never write rules by hand — always use `limacharlie ai generate-detection` |

</details>
